					Gallup StrenghtsQuest Results: adaptability, input, ideation, learner, includer.
				</p>
				<div class='row'>
					<div class='medium-offset-9 medium-3 columns'>
						<div class='logo-wrapper'>
							<img src='images/EZlogoBlackLarge.png' alt='personal logo'>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>


<footer>
	<div class='row'>
		<div class='center'>
		 <p>Elaine Zhou • 2015</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>

<% include templates/scripts %>

</body>
</html>